  <steps>
    <step order="1">Enumerate WP5 FRs from spec.md: FR-25 through FR-37 (13 FRs). For each, locate the acceptance criterion + verification evidence (test output, deploy artifact, prior task completion).</step>
    <step order="2">Enumerate NFR-A1 through NFR-A7 (architectural principles per architecture §2). For each, verify the principle is upheld:
      NFR-A1 (six tiers separated; no implicit cross-tier writes)
      NFR-A2 (JIT retrieval; no file-text stuffing)
      NFR-A3 (citation-bearing trust; requireCitations=true default)
      NFR-A4 (layered context cards ~150-250 tok)
      NFR-A5 (wire-not-build R6 components)
      NFR-A6 (privacy default; T6 audit append-only)
      NFR-A7 (ADR-015 tier-1 logging hygiene)</step>
    <step order="3">Verify architecture §8 tool surface in deployed environment — 8 new tools (`list_session_files`, `get_file_manifest`, `recall_session_file`, `write_session_memory`, `retrieve_matter_memory`, `promote_to_matter_memory`, `get_user_preferences`, `get_org_templates`) + 4 existing (`get_workspace_tab_state`, `update_workspace_tab`, `send_workspace_artifact`, `close_workspace_tab`). Confirm seed (task 092) registered all 8 as `sprk_analysistool` rows.</step>
    <step order="4">Confirm FR-45 regression test (task 080) still green — `PlaybookChatContextProvider.cs:627` invocation continues to fire.</step>
    <step order="5">Verify binding-NEGATIVE rules: grep for `spaarke-insights-index`, `MultiIndexComposer`, `InsightsOrchestrator`, `EvidenceSufficiencyNode`, `GroundingVerifyNode`, `sprk_performancesummary` across `src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/` — chat-memory paths must show ZERO hits.</step>
    <step order="6">Verify BFF publish-size cumulative ≤60 MB; report current size + Phase 4 cumulative delta.</step>
    <step order="7">Compile exit-gate report at `notes/handoffs/105-phase4-exit-gate.md`. Format: per-FR/NFR table with PASS / FAIL / N/A + evidence link.</step>
    <step order="8">If ANY FAIL, escalate per CLAUDE.md §6 — do NOT mark task ✅. Otherwise update TASK-INDEX.md: task 105 → ✅; current-task.md → ready for 110 (Phase 5 start).</step>
  </steps>

